{
  "stem": "26728.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it didn't matter, because our, our commanding officer was also our, ROTC-- RO-- Reserve Officer Training teacher in high school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name was Captain Mitchell, and-- Michaels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I beg your pardon, Captain Michaels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was our company commander in the National Guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The rea-- the motivation was not so much patriotism because the war hadn't even started yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the $5 a month you got to go to the National Guard once a month.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In 1960-- in 1940, President Roosevelt mobilized the National Guards, all the National Guards, all 48 states.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- the Arizona National Guard became part of the 45th Division.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had an option, since I was only 16 at the time-- in September of 1940-- to resign, to tell them the truth.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I could have avoided being called in, being, being activated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But since so many of my friends were, and I was young enough, I thought, I'll go ahead and do my year, and it'll be good for me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And come back and finish my ed-- I had graduated from high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My intentions were to work for a year and then try to go to college at the University of Arizona.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had-- my mother and I had kind of decided that I would-- should be a doctor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was my mama's wish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't feel that strongly about it, but I thought, well, I'll-- I want to go to college if I can.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And why not take, take pre-med, which was available at the university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "OK, in September of 1940, the National Guard was activated with Captain Michaels, as I mentioned-- my high school teacher, ROTC teacher, was our company commander.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I could have gone to him and said-- you know, and he knew that I wasn't 18.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
